<div id="wrapper"><h2><a href="/output/Page2.asp"><img alt="" height="70" src="../files/images/XM_logo.gif" title="XM London Digital Communication" width="162" /></a></h2><h2><img width="190" alt="Case histories" height="80" border="0" src="/files/images/XM_L3_Clients_histories_shdr.gif" /></h2><p><strong>SaBRE - Employer Notification </strong></p><p>Reservists are playing an increasingly important part in maintaining the efficiency of the armed forces and with the changing role of the armed forces into peacekeeping duties Reservists are increasingly being called up.</p><p>Employer Notification is a campaign micro-site built for the Ministry of Defence (MoD) and the SaBRE campaign to inform Employers about changes to notification legislation.</p><p>The micro-site is a part of an integrated information strategy which includes press, brochures and video to inform Employers and Reservists about changes to notification legislation and the implications.</p><p>The site contains comprehensive information of the changes including Frequently Asked Questions, downloadable documents and a contact section which includes data capture.</p><p>The site conforms to Accessibility guidelines.</p><p><a href="http://www.en.mod.uk">http://www.en.mod.uk</a></p><p><img alt="SaBRE Employer Notification" border="0" height="191" src="/files/images/SaBRE Employer Notification 1.jpg" width="275" /></p><p> </p><p><img alt="SaBRE Employer Notification" border="0" height="191" src="/files/images/SaBRE Employer Notification 2.jpg" width="275" /></p><p> </p><p><img alt="SaBRE Employer Notification" border="0" height="191" src="/files/images/SaBRE Employer Notification 3.jpg" width="275" /></p><p> </p><img class="hide" src="/files/images/clear.gif" width="1" height="1" alt="" />
